      "description": "Offering a mechanically sound E46 M3 powered by the high-revving S54 inline-six. This example features a precise 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox and a factory-locked variable differential. Key enthusiast concerns have been proactively managed, including a full VANOS system refresh and structural subframe reinforcement to mitigate fatigue. The chassis remains taut with upgraded bushings, ensuring the hydraulic steering rack provides the signature feedback these cars are known for. It delivers a visceral driving experience with sharp throttle response and a balanced weight distribution.",
